<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Aw Chawian Hitiu</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chawian hitiu Lalmang chungnungpen chu
 A lungsietnan ei na huoia
 Thih leh natna apatin ei hukdam a,
 Dam takin I kimuhtuoh kit chiet tau ui

[V2]
 Aw chawian hitiu, I Hukdampau chu
 Sim leh mal, sak leh thanga kikhensa;
 Kipakin I kimu kit ui, Lalpa minin
 A paknan Aw gi hen, Hallelujah. !

[V3]
 2. Ka hun lamtuoh ui zie welcome phung ahin;
 Ka changlam un ka hun sang ui
 Krista chamna leh lungmuonna chang chiet un
 Kipah nunnawp ni hi hen Krista minin.

[V4]
 3. Kipah nawpna halhna thakin leng kit hen
 Lunggil leh thagau nguisa le
 I chennau thingtang leh I sau gawngsa le
 Lal Krista chawian din no kit hen tuni'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>274</hymn_number>
</song>